    "title": "AI agents will dominate 2026, but who actually benefits? ",
    "preview_text": "AI agents will dominate 2026. \nEveryone can see it coming.\nStartups are racing to build them.\nInvestors are pouring billions into them.\nWorkers will rely on them for everything.\nBut almost no one is",
    "cover_url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HE0a7P1boAAuvsn.jpg",
    "content_state": {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "bogto",
          "text": "AI agents will dominate 2026. ",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "abine",
          "text": "Everyone can see it coming.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "keh6",
          "text": "Startups are racing to build them.\nInvestors are pouring billions into them.\nWorkers will rely on them for everything.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "c5sle",
          "text": "But almost no one is asking the only question that matters:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 22,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "13qgv",
          "text": "Who actually benefits?",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "286p1",
          "text": "Because we’ve seen this before.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "81ed1",
          "text": "The internet created instant information. Google captured it.\nSocial media created community. Meta monetized it.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "1clf7",
          "text": "Now AI agents will create productivity at scale…",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "ehr2u",
          "text": "And the same thing is about to happen again.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "80nuk",
          "text": "Builders will build.\nUsers will use.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 16,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Italic"
            }
          ],
          "key": "dlrqr",
          "text": "But the value?  It flows to the few companies that own the models.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "85eu1",
          "text": "Right now, that’s Big Tech.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "fglgf",
          "text": "Not the builders.\nNot the users.\nNot the people training the systems.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "8d589",
          "text": "And here’s the part most people miss:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 30,
              "offset": 52,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "dj83t",
          "text": "AI isn’t just trained by engineers.\nIt’s trained by millions of people every day. By you.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "bqt2a",
          "text": "Your work.\nYour decisions.\nYour behavior online.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3p11q",
          "text": "Every task you complete improves the system.\nEvery interaction adds signal.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "foums",
          "text": "You are helping build it.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "1mnq5",
          "text": "But you don’t own any of it.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 21,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Italic"
            }
          ],
          "key": "76d0r",
          "text": "So what happens next?",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6bhvm",
          "text": "AI agents don’t just automate tasks.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "8uc51",
          "text": "They replace entire workflows.\nThey compress experience.\nThey reduce the need for labor.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 23,
              "offset": 18,
              "style": "Italic"
            }
          ],
          "key": "3eh9h",
          "text": "And as they scale…they concentrate power.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "blfq9",
          "text": "Not with the people contributing to them, but with the companies that own them.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "7s98m",
          "text": "That’s the real risk. Not AI itself.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 25,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "5ru40",
          "text": "Centralized AI ownership.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "7mqio",
          "text": "Because if AI becomes the interface to the whole internet…",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3cme8",
          "text": "Whoever owns the models\ncontrols the workflows\ncontrols the productivity\ncontrols the value",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "ad6fj",
          "text": "And ultimately…",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 28,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "eclv4",
          "text": "controls the future of work.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4kk40",
          "text": "That system is being built right now.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "enp5o",
          "text": "And most people are contributing to it, without realizing they’re giving everything away.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 0,
              "length": 12,
              "offset": 12
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 12,
              "offset": 12,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "didms",
          "text": "That’s what Action Model aims to change.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2rh6g",
          "text": "A different model. A community-owned model.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "cvfcq",
          "text": "Where the people who train AI, benefit from it.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "f9i6o",
          "text": "Where contribution is rewarded, not extracted.\nWhere ownership is distributed, not concentrated.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "m13s",
          "text": "Because this next wave isn’t about who builds AI.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "a7r9u",
          "text": "It’s about who owns it.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "crgqm",
          "text": "And if we get that wrong…",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "cun25",
          "text": "We don’t just lose upside.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9o2bt",
          "text": "We lose control.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 1,
              "length": 22,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 22,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "7ubea",
          "text": "Download the extension. Start training.\nClaim your stake in the future of AI.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        }
      ],
